<p>One way to compute the digits of <span class="texhtml mvar" style="font-style:italic;">e</span> is with the series<sup id="cite&#95;ref-Finch-2005&#95;65-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Finch-2005-65"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>65<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup>
